<div class="WordSection1">&nbsp;</div>
<div class="WordSection1">Thank you so much for your reply.</div>
<div class="WordSection1">The selected candidate is one of our recruits and employed by us, therefore the risk also lies on Aditro. A lot of work has gone into recruiting, hiring and maintaining her. Then she was presented to you by Aditro.</div>
<div class="WordSection1">In case of unforeseen events that would lead to a termination of placement of the specific consultant, we will also carry related costs and the cost of a new recruitment for you. All of the mentioned and the work we put into all of
