<div class="WordSection1">&nbsp;</div>
<div class="WordSection1">As stated previously we already deducted 8.400 SEK/month and honestly that is really the best we could do and we tried to do our very best to meet you more than half way. Even at this point we are very transparent with you.</div>
<div class="WordSection1">On those grounds, there is the entry you mentioned in the upcharge list.</div>
<div class="WordSection1">The margines after the deduction are really low for us.</div>
<div class="WordSection1">I’m almost certain that even if we take this higher up in our management, the changes would be none or very marginal and it will prolong the process as many of our colleagues have already left for summer vacation.</div>
<div class="WordSection1">&nbsp;</div>
<div class="WordSection1">Still I would really love for us to talk further on Teams and discuss face to face.</div>
